==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Quadroon
<hw>Quad*roon"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.
<ets>quarteron</ets>, or Sp. <ets>cuarteron</ets>. See <er>Quarter</er>
a fourth part, and cf. <er>Quarteron</er>.]</ety> <def>The offspring of
a mulatto and a white person; a person quarter-blooded.</def>
<altsp>[Written also <asp>quarteron</asp>, <asp>quarteroon</asp>, and
<asp>quateron</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Quadroxide</ent>⟦br⟧
